  • java.lang.Object
    • model.AbstractVehicle

    Atv, Bicycle, Car, Human, Taxi, Truck

    public abstract class AbstractVehicle
extends java.lang.Object
implements Vehicle
    This abstract class manages all the common methods for all vehicle types.
